    A dataset containing the IPC base 2010 only for the Montevideo region

    ipc_base2010_mdeo

    Format

    A data frame with 120 rows and 2 variables:

    fecha

    date from 2011 to 2019

    indice

    IPC

    Source

    https://www.gub.uy/instituto-nacional-estadistica/
